flowchart TD
    A([Content brief: topic, tone, keywords, length]) --> B[Match brief to prompt template]
    B --> C[Assemble prompt with brief parameters]
    C --> D{Cache hit?}
    D -- Hit --> K
    D -- Miss --> E[LLM generation: produce draft]
    E --> F[Automated quality checks: length, keywords, readability]
    F --> G{Quality checks pass?}
    G -- Fail --> H[Regenerate with corrective constraints]
    H --> E
    G -- Pass --> I[Moderation screening]
    I --> J{Moderation pass?}
    J -- Fail --> L([Return policy refusal to requester])
    J -- Pass --> K[Route by content risk level]
    K --> M{High-stakes content?}
    M -- Yes --> N[Human review queue]
    N --> O{Reviewer decision}
    O -- Approve --> P[Publish to CMS or downstream system]
    O -- Revise --> Q[Add reviewer notes to prompt]
    Q --> E
    M -- No --> P
    P --> R([Content published])
